author: ANTHONY McCARTNEY
title: Judge dismisses copyright infringement case against Jay Z
text:
Celebrate Majestic's 90th birthday 
On Saturday, Nov. 14, at 8 p.m., the Majestic Theater will celebrate its 90th Anniversary with Neil Berg's widely acclaimed "100 Years of Broadway", a musical revue of Broadway's most celebrated shows featuring a dazzling cast of five Broadway stars accompanied by an all-star New York band. Posted: October 22
